<comment datatype='string'>We inferred that &lt;i&gt;ytfK&lt;/i&gt; is expressed as a monocistronic transcription unit, based on the genomic context of the gene. It is isolated in the forward direction, and the surrounding genes are encoded in the reverse direction.
